PrecisAppointment of CLAIRE MORRIS of Fredericton, New Brunswick, as Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources Development, to hold office during pleasure, and as commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Vice-Chairperson of the Commission, effective December 1, 1998.
